     H            Y.
     F** AM#R21 *********************************************
     F* LOADING                                             *
     F*    LEC              2018.09.17                      *
     F*    LEC  2018.09.17  ADD LOGIC TO VERIFY MANIFEST OVR*
     F*    LEC  2019.03.13  ADD LOGIC FOR BLOWOUTS &        *
     F*                     FREIGHT DAMAGE SCANS            *
     F*    LEC  2019.03.20  ADD LOGIC FOR SHIP TIME         *
     F*    LEC  2019.06.26  ADD LOGIC FOR EXCEPTIONS        *
     F*    LEC  2020.08.18  SEND MANIFEST TO HULFT SQL      *
     F*    LEC  2020.10.16  ADD FUNC KEY TO SEND TRUCK COMPL*
     F*    LEC  2022.01.10  CHG TO CALL SER. PARTS LOAD PGM *
     F*    LEC  2024.03.14  ADD CHECK FOR COMPLETE PALLET   *
     F*******************************************************
     FAM#PW21 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FALBPL30 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAM#PL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAL#PP21 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAM#PL21 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1  15 65
     E                    ROUT       10  1
     E                    TICK       12  1
      *
     IB2D         DS
     I                                        1  19 BAR01
      *
      * TRUCK TICKET QR BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1  25 TT
     I                                        1   7 TTSURT
     I                                        8  15 TTSHDT
     I                                        8  11 TTSHYY
     I                                       12  13 TTSHMM
     I                                       14  15 TTSHDD
     I                                       16  21 TTSHTM
     I                                       16  17 TTSHHH
     I                                       18  19 TTSHMN
     I                                       20  21 TTSHSS
     I                                        8  19 TTDTTM
     I                                       22  25 TTFILR
     IMAN         DS
     I                                        1  25 MAN01
     I                                       26  50 MAN02
     I                                       44  44 MFSIDE
      *
      * 2D MANIFEST BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1  50 MF
     I                                        1   5 MFNAMC
     I                                        3   5 MFTYPE
     I                                        6  10 MFSUPP
     I                                       11  12 MFDOCK
     I                                       13  24 MFORD#
     I                                       25  33 MFMRTE
     I                                       34  36 MFSDCK
     I                                       37  38 MFPALT
     I                                       39  40 MFMROS
     I                                       41  44 MFSKID
     I                                       45  50 MFFILR
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 SHDT
     I                                        1   4 SHYY
     I I            '/'                       5   5 SLSH1
     I                                        6   7 SHMM
     I I            '/'                       8   8 SLSH2
     I                                        9  10 SHDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 SHTM
     I                                        1   2 SHHH
     I I            ':'                       3   3 COLN1
     I                                        4   5 SHMN
     I I            ':'                       6   6 COLN2
     I                                        7   8 SHSS
      *
      * manifest totals for error message - problem info
     I            DS
     I                                        1  25 MFTMSG
     I                                        2  12 TLPGM
     I                                       15  170TLPACK
     I                                       20  220TLORD
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           WORKER  6
     C                     PARM           WUSRID 10
     C                     PARM           PCMD    2
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     EXSR #SB100
     C           DSPSW     DOUEQ'99'
     C                     EXSR #SB200
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     EXSR #SB300
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * INZ                                                *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB100    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVELWORKER    WKCD    60
     C           WKCD      CHAINALBPL30              61
     C           *IN61     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ALWKNM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVEL'01'      DSPSW   2
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PCMD    2
     C                     CLEARB2D
      *
     CSR         ESB100    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB200    BEGSR
      *
     C           DSPSW     DOWEQ'01'
     C                     EXSR #SB210
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           DSPSW     DOWEQ'02'
     C                     EXSR #SB220
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESB200    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *　⒳�痧���Ј灈�聭饎�　　　　　　　　　　　　�
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB210    BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP01
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE  3
     C                     SETOF                     3199
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C           *IN03     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'03'      PCMD    2
     C                     MOVEL'99'      DSPSW   2
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN09     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'AM#C17'
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           B2D       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,1      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELB2D       TT
     C                     MOVE '00'      TTSHTM
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    EXPEDT  1
      * if this an expedite route, skip check...
      *    else check truck ticket.
     C           'EX-'     SCAN TT:1      POS     30
     C           POS       IFGT *ZERO
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       EXPEDT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   TTSHTM
     C                     ELSE
      *
      * check truck ticket date and time for blanks.
      * if date and time contains a blank it's invalid.
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   TICK
      *
     C                     MOVEATTDTTM    TICK
     C                     DO   12        X
     C           TICK,X    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,11     MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *�����束
     C                     EXSR #SB920
     C                     MOVEL'Truck'   D1BIN
     C                     MOVELTTSURT    D1IAFB
      *
     C                     MOVELTTSHYY    SHYY
     C                     MOVELTTSHMM    SHMM
     C                     MOVELTTSHDD    SHDD
     C                     MOVELSHDT      D1SHDT
      *
     C                     MOVELTTSHHH    SHHH
     C                     MOVELTTSHMN    SHMN
     C                     MOVELTTSHSS    SHSS
     C                     MOVELSHTM      D1SHTM
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP2LDTL    D1SUMI
     C                     MOVEL'/'       D1SRSH
     C                     Z-ADDP2TOTL    D1TOTL
      *
     C                     MOVELTTSHHH    SHHH
     C                     MOVELTTSHMN    SHMN
     C                     MOVELTTSHSS    SHSS
     C                     MOVELSHTM      D1SHTM
      *
      * if no records for route/ship date found, then display error
     C           P2TOTL    IFEQ 0
     C           EXPEDT    ANDNE'Y'
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,7      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     CLEARB2D
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL'02'      DSPSW   2
     C                     CLEARMAN
      *
     CSR         ESB210    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *　⒳�痧���樠肁瘌�沜�Č�　　　　　　　　　　�
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB220    BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP02
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     SETOF                     3199
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
      * if f3, then go back to screen 1.
     C           *IN03     IFEQ '1'
     C                     CLEARB2D
     C                     MOVEL'01'      DSPSW   2
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if f4, then display delete manifest screen and recalculate totals.
     C           *IN04     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR #SB400
     C                     EXSR #SB920
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if f6, then call exception selection program,
      *        scan selected exceptions,
      *        recalculate all totals.
     C           *IN06     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'AM#R29'
     C                     PARM           EXCODE
     C                     PARM           EXTYPE 30
      *
     C           EXCODE    IFNE *BLANKS
     C                     EXSR #SB600
     C                     EXSR #SB920
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if f10, call pgm to create Service Parts Truck/Load info...
     C           *IN10     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR #SPART
     C                     MOVEL'01'      DSPSW
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * check manifest screen for errors.
     C           MAN       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WKHNTE  2
     C                     MOVELMAN       MF
      *
      * check namc destination code exists in M/F or it's an Export.
     C           MFNAMC    CHAINAL#PP21              44
     C           *IN44     IFEQ *ON
     C           MFTYPE    ANDNE'EXP'
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,9      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * check to verify this manifest has not already been entered.
      * then if manifest is new, check to verify if manifest is in packing file.
     C                     EXSR #SB710
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     EXSR #SB720
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * treat these errors differently because they need to have the option
      * to override the error and let them be added if TL says it's okay.
      * could be supplemental order, last minute add-on.
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
      *
     C           MSG       IFEQ ER,4
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN   1
      *********  MSG       OREQ ER,6
     C                     EXSR #SB777
     C                     ELSE
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     GOTO ESB220
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * no errors, so write to loading out-file and recalculate totals.
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL'OK'      WKHNTE  2
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     EXSR #SKID
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     EXSR #SB920
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP2LDTL    D1SUMI
     C                     Z-ADDP2TOTL    D1TOTL
     C                     Z-ADDP2OVTL    D1OVTL
     C                     Z-ADDP2EXTL    D1EXTL
      *
      * total up # of manifests scanned and compare to total manifests
     C           P2LDTL    ADD  P2OVTL    TLSCAN  40
     C                     ADD  P2EXTL    TLSCAN
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB220    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * WRITE ERROR TO LOADING OUT-FILE AND LOCK DISPLAY.  *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB229    BEGSR
      *
     C           WKHNTE    IFEQ 'NG'
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     Z-ADD3         P1PGM
     C                     MOVELMSG       P1ERR
     C                     MOVELW#PGM     P1PID
     C                     MOVELWORKER    P1KOME    P
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     P1DTTM
     C                     CALL 'AM#R09'                   LOCK
     C                     PARM           P1PGM   20
     C                     PARM           P1ERR  25
     C                     PARM           P1PID  10
     C                     PARM           P1KOME 10
     C                     PARM           P1DTTM 140
     C                     ELSE
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
      *
     CSR         ESB229    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *　⒳�痧���痡瘏�黬�砑ⓓ���鰖槖　　　　　　�
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB400    BEGSR
      *
     C           *IN03     DOUEQ*ON
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP04
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     SETOF                     3199
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      * F3 to cancel delete and go back to screen 2.
     C           *IN03     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVEL'02'      DSPSW
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * verify that manifest has been scanned to load out-file.
     C           MAN       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'A'       MFSIDE
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN26
     C           MAN       SETLLAM#PL21
     C           *IN26     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           MAN       READEAM#PL21                  26
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
     C           R2SURT    ANDEQTTSURT
     C           R2SHID    ANDEQTTSHDT
     C           R2SHIT    ANDEQTTSHTM
     C           R2SKJY    ANDEQ' '
     C           R2HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * if manifest was not found in loading out-file, display error.
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if manifest was found...
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
      *
      *  and it matches the route/ship date, then delete
     C           R2SURT    IFEQ TTSURT
     C           R2SHID    ANDEQTTSHDT
     C           R2SHIT    ANDEQTTSHTM
     C                     MOVEL'D'       R2SKJY
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     R2SKHZ
     C                     UPDATAM#PP211
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ELSE
      *  if it doesn't match, then unlock record and display error.
     C                     UNLCKAM#PL21                31
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESB400    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *　⒳�痧����痮�ĝ�濰�　　　　　　　　　　　�
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB600    BEGSR
      *
     C           *IN03     DOUEQ*ON
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     COUNT   30
     C                     MOVELEXCODE    EXCD    3
     C                     MOVELEXTYPE    HEADNG 30
     C                     CALL 'AM#R22E'
     C                     PARM           TTSURT
     C                     PARM           TTSHDT
     C                     PARM           TTSHTM
     C                     PARM           EXCD
     C                     PARM           COUNT
     C                     Z-ADDCOUNT     D1CNT
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP06
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     SETOF                     3199
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      * F3 to cancel exception and go back to screen 2.
     C           *IN03     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVEL'02'      DSPSW
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * verify that manifest has been scanned to load out-file.
     C           MAN       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'A'       MFSIDE
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN26
     C           MAN       SETLLAM#PL21
     C           *IN26     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           MAN       READEAM#PL21                  26
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
     C           R2SURT    ANDEQTTSURT
     C           R2SHID    ANDEQTTSHDT
     C           R2SHIT    ANDEQTTSHTM
     C           R2SKJY    ANDEQ' '
     C           R2HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * if manifest was not found in loading out-file, display error.
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if manifest was found...
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
      *
      *  and it matches the route/ship date, then delete
     C           R2SURT    IFEQ TTSURT
     C           R2SHID    ANDEQTTSHDT
     C           R2SHIT    ANDEQTTSHTM
     C                     MOVELEXCODE    R2EXCD
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     R2KOHZ
     C                     Z-ADDSTIME     R2KOTI
     C                     MOVELWORKER    R2KOME    P
     C                     UPDATAM#PP211
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ELSE
      *  if it doesn't match, then unlock record and display error.
     C                     UNLCKAM#PL21                31
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     EXSR #SB999
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    MSG
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESB600    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * ERROR ON SCREEN BUT NOT LOCKABLE.                  *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB999    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVELMSG       P1ERR
     C                     CALL 'AM#R08'
     C                     PARM           P1ERR  25
      *
     C                     MOVEL'NG'      WKHNTE
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C           LOGYN     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR #SB500
     C                     MOVE 'N'       LOGYN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB999    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * END PROGRAM.                                       *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB300    BEGSR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     CSR         ESB300    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * WRITE TO LOADING OUT-FILE AM#PP21.                 *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB500    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARAM#PP211
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     R2KOHZ
     C                     Z-ADDSTIME     R2KOTI
     C                     MOVELWORKER    R2KOME
     C                     MOVELW#PGM     R2KPGM
     C                     Z-ADDSDATE     R2SSHZ
     C                     Z-ADDSTIME     R2SSTI
     C                     MOVELWORKER    R2USCD
     C                     MOVELALWKNM    R2USNM
     C                     MOVELWKHNTE    R2HNTE
     C                     MOVELMSG       R2ERR
     C                     MOVE MFTMSG    R2ERR
      *
     C                     MOVELTT        R2TICK
     C                     MOVELTTSURT    R2SURT    P
     C                     MOVELTTSHDT    R2SHID
     C                     MOVELTTSHTM    R2SHIT
     C           EXPEDT    IFNE 'Y'
     C                     MOVE '00'      R2SHIT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'A'       MFSIDE
     C                     MOVELMAN       R22D
     C                     MOVELMFNAMC    R2NAMC
     C                     MOVELMFSUPP    R2SUPP
     C                     MOVELMFDOCK    R2NUKE
     C                     MOVELMFORD#    R2ORDN
     C                     MOVELMFMRTE    R2MRTE
     C                     MOVELMFSDCK    R2DOCK
     C                     MOVELMFPALT    R2PLTC
     C                     MOVELMFMROS    R2MRSO
     C                     MOVELMFSKID    R2SKID
     C                     MOVELMFFILR    R2FIL2
      *
     C           F5        IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVELF5        R2F5OV
     C                     MOVELWCODE     R2USCD
     C                     MOVELWNAME     R2USNM
     C                     MOVELR1SURT    R2PSUR
     C                     MOVELR1SHID    R2PSHD
     C                     MOVELR1SHIT    R2PSHT
     C                     MOVELF5ERMG    R2ERR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELEXCODE    R2EXCD
      *
     C                     WRITEAM#PP211
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    F5
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   MFTMSG
      *
     CSR         ESB500    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  CHECK TO VERIFY NOT ALREADY SCANNED.              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB710    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVE 'A'       MFSIDE
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN26
     C           MAN       SETLLAM#PL21
     C           *IN26     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           MAN       READEAM#PL21             N    26
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
     C           R2SKJY    ANDEQ' '
     C           R2HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * if already scanned, set error message.
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB710    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  CHECK TO VERIFY THIS MANIFEST WAS SCANNED IN      *
      *  PACKING PROGRAM.                                  *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB720    BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETOF                     26
     C                     MOVE 'A'       MFSIDE
     C           MAN       SETLLAM#PL05
     C           *IN26     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           MAN       READEAM#PL05                  26
      *
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *OFF
     C           R1SKJY    ANDEQ' '
     C           R1HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C           R1EXCD    ANDNE'12'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * if not scanned in packing out-file, set error message.
     C           *IN26     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,6      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   R1SURT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   R1SHID
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   R1SHIT
     C                     GOTO ESB720
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * get pallet totals...packed and ordered...
     C                     EXSR #PALT
      *
      * if total packed is less than total ordered, incomplete...
     C           TPACK     IFLT TORD
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,14     MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    EXCODE
     C                     GOTO ESB720
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
      * if this is an expedite or urgent route, then skip route check.
     C           R1SURT    IFEQ 'EXPDIT'
     C           R1SURT    OREQ 'URGENT'
     C           R1SURT    OREQ 'UNPLAN'
     C           EXPEDT    OREQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVELER,12     MSG
     C                     MOVEL'18'      EXCODE
     C                     GOTO ESB720
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if scanned in packing out-file but route NOT = truck ticket
      *    Route Run can be different but NOT Route, so set error message.
     C           R1SURT    IFNE TTSURT
     C                     EXSR CHKRTE
     C           R1ROUT    IFNE TTROUT
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,10     MSG
     C                     GOTO ESB720
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if scanned in packing out-file but route/ship date NOT = truck ticket
      *    set error message.
     C           R1SURT    IFNE TTSURT
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,4      MSG
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       LOGYN
     C                     MOVEL'18 '     EXCODE
     C                     GOTO ESB720
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           R1SHID    IFNE TTSHDT
     C           R1SHIT    ORNE TTSHTM
     C                     MOVEL'23 '     EXCODE
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       F5
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB720    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  CALL PGM TO DISPLAY ERROR AND ACCEPT OVERRIDE     *
      *    OR CANCEL.                                      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB777    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    F5      1
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   WCODE  10
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   WNAME  20
     C                     CALL 'AM#R23'
     C                     PARM           MSG
     C                     PARM           F5
     C                     PARM           WCODE
     C                     PARM           WNAME
      *
      * if user pressed f5 to accept override
     C           F5        IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVELMSG       F5ERMG 25
     C                     MOVEL'18'      EXCODE
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     ELSE
     C                     CLEARMAN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * NUMBER OF MANIFESTS                                *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB920    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2TOTL
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2LDTL
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2OVTL
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2EXTL
     C                     CALL 'AM#R22'
     C                     PARM           TTSURT
     C                     PARM           TTSHDT
     C                     PARM           TTSHTM
     C                     PARM           P2TOTL  30
     C                     PARM           P2LDTL  30
     C                     PARM           P2OVTL  30
     C                     PARM           P2EXTL  30
      *
     C           P2OVTL    IFGT *ZERO
     C                     MOVEL'OVR ='   D1OVRT
     C                     Z-ADDP2OVTL    D1OVTL
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   D1OVRT
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     D1OVTL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           P2EXTL    IFGT *ZERO
     C                     MOVEL'EXCP='   D1EXCP
     C                     Z-ADDP2EXTL    D1EXTL
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   D1EXCP
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     D1EXTL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB920    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * BLANK OUT THE RUN PORTION OF THE SUB-ROUTE FROM    *
      * THE TRUCK TICKET AND THE SKID MANIFEST             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         CHKRTE    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ROUT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   TTROUT 10
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   R1ROUT 10
      *
     C                     MOVEATTSURT    ROUT
     C                     DO   10        X       30
     C           ROUT,X    IFGE '0'
     C           ROUT,X    ANDLE'9'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    ROUT,X
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     MOVEAROUT      TTROUT
      *
     C                     MOVEAR1SURT    ROUT
     C                     DO   10        X
     C           ROUT,X    IFGE '0'
     C           ROUT,X    ANDLE'9'
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    ROUT,X
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     MOVEAROUT      R1ROUT
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CALL PGM TO SCAN SERVICE PARTS TO TRUCK TICKET     *
      *  PASS TT INFO TO PGM.                             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SPART    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CALL 'AM#C21SP'
     C                     PARM           WORKER
     C                     PARM           WUSRID
     C                     PARM           TT
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CREATE AND SEND SKID BUILD TO SCS.                 *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SKID     BEGSR
      *
     C                     CALL 'AM#R413'
     C                     PARM           R22D
     C                     PARM           WORKER
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * CHECK TO MAKE SURE PALLET IS COMPLETE.             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           #PALT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   MFTMSG
      *
      * check pallet to make sure it's completely packed...
     C                     MOVEL'AM#R02O' TLPGM
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     TPACK   30
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     TORD    30
     C                     MOVELMFDOCK    DOCK4   4 P
     C                     CALL 'AM#R02O'
     C                     PARM           MFNAMC
     C                     PARM           MFORD#
     C                     PARM           DOCK4
     C                     PARM           MFPALT
     C                     PARM           MFMROS
     C                     PARM           TORD
     C                     PARM           TPACK
      *
      * if no total for pallet, check supplemental files...
      ********   TPACK     IFEQ *ZERO
      ********   TORD      ANDEQ*ZERO
      ********             MOVEL'AM#R02S' TLPGM
      ********             CALL 'AM#R02S'
      ********             PARM           MFNAMC
      ********             PARM           MFDOCK
      ********             PARM           MFORD#
      ********             PARM           MF
      ********             PARM           TORD
      ********             PARM           TPACK
      ********             ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDTORD      TLORD
     C                     Z-ADDTPACK     TLPACK
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
**
INPUT TRUCK TICKET.
INPUT MANIFEST BARCODE.
SCANNED ALL.
TRUCK/SHIP DATE MISMATCH.
ALREADY SCANNED.
MANIFEST NOT IN PACKING.
NO TRUCK DATA IN PACKING.
MAN# NOT SCANNED TO TRUCK.
INVALID MANIFEST BARCODE.
TRUCK ROUTE MISMATCH.
INVALID TRUCK TICKET
URGENT/EXPEDITE ADDED.
1234567890123456789012345
PACKING INCOMPLETE

